description: Keep an eye on the roads of Brandenton, Florida for The Traveling Kitchen, in which you will find all your favorite eclectic yet classic fare, like Breakfast Burritos, Burgers, Latin-style Pulled Pork Sandwiches, and so much more. And of course, it all tastes fantastic.You’ll be sure to come back to try everything they’ve cooked, because, as they guarantee: “One taste and you’re hooked!”
name: TK Grill
